# Regular Expressions for Data Validation

## Description
This project demonstrates how to use Python regular expressions to validate
email addresses, Indian mobile numbers, and strong passwords.

## Tools Used
- Python
- re module
- VS Code

## Features
- Email validation
- Indian mobile number validation
- Strong password validation
- User input handling
- Edge case testing

## How to Run
1. Clone the repository
2. Run `python regex_validation.py`
3. Enter inputs when prompted

## Outcome
This task helps understand real-world input validation using regex.
